      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey i have a question about my insulin. im type 1 and i usually take my basal dose in the evening but i barely ate anything for dinner tonight, like just a few bites of a salad. is it okay if i just skip the dose tonight so my blood sugar doesn't crash too low? feels safer that way since i didn't really eat much.",
